<a href="http://www.isinj.com/mt-usamo/Secrets%20in%20Inequalities%20(volume%201)%20Pham%20Kim%20Hung.pdf">Secrets in Inequalities (volume 1) Pham Kim Hung.pdf</a></div>
<div style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; orphans: 2; widows: 2;">
<a href="http://www.isinj.com/mt-usamo/Geometric%20Problems%20on%20Maxima%20and%20Minima%20-%20Titu%20Andreescu,%20Oleg%20Mushkarov,%20Luchezar%20Stoyanov.pdf">Geometric Problems on Maxima and Minima - Titu Andreescu, Oleg Mushkarov, Luchezar Stoyanov.pdf</a></div>
